-- Euro Extends Decline Against U.S. Dollar, Erases Gain Versus Japanese Yen
-- Daniel Tilles
-- 2010-06-28T07:49:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/euro-extends-decline-against-u-s-dollar-erases-gain-versus-japanese-yen.html

          
          
             The euro extended its drop against
the dollar and erased a gain versus the yen.  
 The 16-nation currency fell as much as 0.2 percent to
$1.2349, before trading at $1.2352 as of 8:47 a.m. in London.
The euro was at 110.38 yen, after rising to 110.82 yen.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Daniel Tilles in London at 
 dtilles@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  
     
       
     
           
                           
                 
                 
                                       
                                   
               
                        
           
